summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 23W, Page 28 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (86300) to rezone certain property in Section 32, Township 26 North, Range 4 East W.M., from Single Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone.
